client.communication

Class ServerProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.communication.ServerProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IServer

    public class ServerProxy
extends java.lang.Object
implements IServer
    A proxy that acts as the server to the client. Contains all the methods that can be called on the server. Each method bundles the given variables and gives it to the ClientCommunicator to send through the HTTP protocol.
    Author:
    jchip
